    <string name="expense_help_line1">• This screen shows all meetings you’ve created, sorted by date.</string>
    <string name="expense_help_line2">• Tap a meeting to view its details, edit expenses or modify groups.</string>
    <string name="expense_help_line3">• Delete a meeting using the trash icon.</string>
    <string name="expense_help_line4">• From a meeting’s details, you can share a summary with the share icon.</string>
