    <string name="create_meeting_help_title">How to create a meeting?</string>
    <string name="create_meeting_help_line1">• Give your meeting a name and add the participating groups (families, friends, etc.).</string>
    <string name="create_meeting_help_line2">• Each group can have a name and a number of people associated.</string>
    <string name="create_meeting_help_line3">• The group size will be used later to divide expenses proportionally.</string>
    <string name="create_meeting_help_line4">• If you want to add a particular person, leave the group size at 1</string>
    <string name="create_meeting_help_line5">• You will be able to add and edit expenses once the meeting is created.</string>


