    <string name="help_title_expense">How to record an expense?</string>
    <string name="help_expense_1">• Write a brief description of the expense (e.g. \'Pizza\', \'Ticket\', \'Coca-Cola\').</string>
    <string name="help_expense_2">• Indicate how much each group contributed.</string>
    <string name="help_expense_3">• Then, select how many people from each group consumed the expense.</string>
    <string name="help_expense_4">• The total is calculated automatically from the contributions.</string>
    <string name="help_expense_5">• The expense will be split proportionally based on consumption.</string>


