    <string name="dialog_meeting_info_title">About the meeting</string>
    <string name="info_meeting_line1">• Here you can see a summary of the meeting with date, total spent, and expenses.</string>
    <string name="info_meeting_line2">• You can edit or delete expenses, or add new ones.</string>
    <string name="info_meeting_line3">• You can also modify the groups: change name, number of people, or remove them.</string>
    <string name="info_meeting_line4">• The debts section shows who owes whom, based on how much each group paid and consumed.</string>
    <string name="info_meeting_line5">• The calculation is automatic and proportional to the number of people who consumed from each group.</string>
    <string name="info_meeting_line6">• You can use the share button to send the summary via message, email, or any compatible app. Perfect to split expenses with friends.</string>


